{"tid":669296,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"電盈新推OTT平台","createTime":"2018-05-18T10:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T10:37:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"32305f46d6de2ffb2b325cace06bb8750b18854e","tid":669296,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180518/20394666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F20394666&d=6AIAJUJho3TNnEQBKE8JqQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=9a6ca530\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F20394666&h=ab19ee31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180518/20394666</a><br />\n<br />\n電盈新推OTT平台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180518/large/17677529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180518%2Flarge%2F17677529.jpg&h=b5a98d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■電盈推出全新流動多媒體體育及娛樂服務OTT平台NowE。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】電盈（008）昨推出全新流動多媒體體育及娛樂服務OTT平台NowE，一App睇盡旗下體育、電影、劇集，包括HBO GO、Now爆谷台、Viu及ViuTV，綜合娛樂組合每月98元，無合約，新客戶免費試用一個月。<br />\n<br />\n另有世界盃通行證980元及一日通行證98元。NowE用戶亦可利用7月推出的「即租即睇」服務，欣賞最新荷里活及亞洲猛片及演唱會。Now E本月下旬起於蘋果App Store及Google Play下載，一次最多可支援五部裝置，兩個裝置同時觀看。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n油價創近四年新高<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n茂宸購體外受孕業務　引入微醫"}]}